{"title":"Projects","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Projects"},"headingText":"Latest Articles","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n<style>\n#title-block-header { display: none; }\n</style>\n\n<p class=\"eyebrow\">Work</p>\n\n<p class=\"headline\">Disciplined where it counts. Curious everywhere else.</p>\n\n<p class=\"lede\">A few things I've built recently. Unless noted otherwise, the data\nengineering, modelling, and analysis are mine end to end.</p>\n\n<div class=\"project-list\">\n\n<div class=\"project-list-item\">\n<a class=\"project-list-thumb-link\" href=\"projects/aemo-exogenous-shock.html\">\n<img src=\"images/ols_vs_hybrid_threshold_comparison.png\" class=\"project-list-thumb\">\n</a>\n<div class=\"project-list-tags\">\n<span class=\"status-badge status-complete\">Complete</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Forecasting (Econometric)</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">One-Off</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"project-list-title\"><a href=\"projects/aemo-exogenous-shock.html\">Reacting to an Exogenous Shock Mid-Forecast</a></h3>\n<p class=\"project-list-desc\">A demo forecasting model showing how to detect and respond to an exogenous shock partway through a forecast horizon, using AEMO electricity demand data.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"project-list-item\">\n<a class=\"project-list-thumb-link\" href=\"projects/chronicling-america.html\">\n<img src=\"images/wedding-placeholder.png\" class=\"project-list-thumb\">\n</a>\n<div class=\"project-list-tags\">\n<span class=\"status-badge status-complete\">Complete</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">ETL Pipelines</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Historical Recipe Series</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"project-list-title\"><a href=\"projects/chronicling-america.html\">Chronicling America API Migration</a></h3>\n<p class=\"project-list-desc\">Migrating a bulk newspaper data pipeline to a new API after the legacy access method was deprecated.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"project-list-item\">\n<a class=\"project-list-thumb-link\" href=\"projects/ocr-assistance-model.html\">\n<img src=\"images/wedding-placeholder.png\" class=\"project-list-thumb\">\n</a>\n<div class=\"project-list-tags\">\n<span class=\"status-badge status-in-progress\">In Progress</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Historical Recipe Series</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Python</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"project-list-title\"><a href=\"projects/ocr-assistance-model.html\">Training an OCR Assistance Model</a></h3>\n<p class=\"project-list-desc\">A model-in-progress to assist OCR correction on historical newspaper scans, as part of the Historical Recipe Series.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"section-divider\"></div>\n\n\n<p class=\"headline\">A few notes on the work, written as I go.</p>\n\n<div class=\"article-teasers\">\n<div class=\"article-teaser position-relative\">\n<h3><a class=\"stretched-link\" href=\"articles/reflections-on-vibe-coding.html\">Reflections on Vibe Coding: Get the Craftsman a Duck that Talks Back</a></h3>\n<p>What changed when I pointed AI at a from-scratch build versus a legacy API migration - and what the research says about why.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article-teaser position-relative\">\n<h3><a class=\"stretched-link\" href=\"articles/exogenous-shocks-in-practice.html\">Lorem Ipsum Dolor Sit Amet Consectetur</a></h3>\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"view-all-link\"><a href=\"articles.html\">View all articles &rarr;</a></p>\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n<style>\n#title-block-header { display: none; }\n</style>\n\n<p class=\"eyebrow\">Work</p>\n\n<p class=\"headline\">Disciplined where it counts. Curious everywhere else.</p>\n\n<p class=\"lede\">A few things I've built recently. Unless noted otherwise, the data\nengineering, modelling, and analysis are mine end to end.</p>\n\n<div class=\"project-list\">\n\n<div class=\"project-list-item\">\n<a class=\"project-list-thumb-link\" href=\"projects/aemo-exogenous-shock.html\">\n<img src=\"images/ols_vs_hybrid_threshold_comparison.png\" class=\"project-list-thumb\">\n</a>\n<div class=\"project-list-tags\">\n<span class=\"status-badge status-complete\">Complete</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Forecasting (Econometric)</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">One-Off</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"project-list-title\"><a href=\"projects/aemo-exogenous-shock.html\">Reacting to an Exogenous Shock Mid-Forecast</a></h3>\n<p class=\"project-list-desc\">A demo forecasting model showing how to detect and respond to an exogenous shock partway through a forecast horizon, using AEMO electricity demand data.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"project-list-item\">\n<a class=\"project-list-thumb-link\" href=\"projects/chronicling-america.html\">\n<img src=\"images/wedding-placeholder.png\" class=\"project-list-thumb\">\n</a>\n<div class=\"project-list-tags\">\n<span class=\"status-badge status-complete\">Complete</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">ETL Pipelines</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Historical Recipe Series</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"project-list-title\"><a href=\"projects/chronicling-america.html\">Chronicling America API Migration</a></h3>\n<p class=\"project-list-desc\">Migrating a bulk newspaper data pipeline to a new API after the legacy access method was deprecated.</p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"project-list-item\">\n<a class=\"project-list-thumb-link\" href=\"projects/ocr-assistance-model.html\">\n<img src=\"images/wedding-placeholder.png\" class=\"project-list-thumb\">\n</a>\n<div class=\"project-list-tags\">\n<span class=\"status-badge status-in-progress\">In Progress</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Historical Recipe Series</span>\n<span class=\"tag-chip\">Python</span>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"project-list-title\"><a href=\"projects/ocr-assistance-model.html\">Training an OCR Assistance Model</a></h3>\n<p class=\"project-list-desc\">A model-in-progress to assist OCR correction on historical newspaper scans, as part of the Historical Recipe Series.</p>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"section-divider\"></div>\n\n## Latest Articles\n\n<p class=\"headline\">A few notes on the work, written as I go.</p>\n\n<div class=\"article-teasers\">\n<div class=\"article-teaser position-relative\">\n<h3><a class=\"stretched-link\" href=\"articles/reflections-on-vibe-coding.html\">Reflections on Vibe Coding: Get the Craftsman a Duck that Talks Back</a></h3>\n<p>What changed when I pointed AI at a from-scratch build versus a legacy API migration - and what the research says about why.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"article-teaser position-relative\">\n<h3><a class=\"stretched-link\" href=\"articles/exogenous-shocks-in-practice.html\">Lorem Ipsum Dolor Sit Amet Consectetur</a></h3>\n<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"view-all-link\"><a href=\"articles.html\">View all articles &rarr;</a></p>\n"},"formats":{"html":{"identifier":{"display-name":"HTML","target-format":"html","base-format":"html"},"execute":{"fig-width":7,"fig-height":5,"fig-format":"retina","fig-dpi":96,"df-print":"default","error":false,"eval":true,"cache":null,"freeze":false,"echo":true,"output":true,"warning":true,"include":true,"keep-md":false,"keep-ipynb":false,"ipynb":null,"enabled":null,"daemon":null,"daemon-restart":false,"debug":false,"ipynb-filters":[],"ipynb-shell-interactivity":null,"plotly-connected":true,"engine":"markdown"},"render":{"keep-tex":false,"keep-typ":false,"keep-source":false,"keep-hidden":false,"prefer-html":false,"output-divs":true,"output-ext":"html","fig-align":"default","fig-pos":null,"fig-env":null,"code-fold":"none","code-overflow":"scroll","code-link":false,"code-line-numbers":false,"code-tools":false,"tbl-colwidths":"auto","merge-includes":true,"inline-includes":false,"preserve-yaml":false,"latex-auto-mk":true,"latex-auto-install":true,"latex-clean":true,"latex-min-runs":1,"latex-max-runs":10,"latex-makeindex":"makeind